PrecisAcceptance of an Instrument (DESIGNATION AND REVOCATION OF SURRENDER) wherein the BOSTON BAR BAND surrenders, for a term of 60 years, some 60 hectares of land on Kopchitchin Indian Reserve No. 2, in British Columbia, for commercial and light industrial purposes, and revokes the surrender it made in 1893.
